strings: <voice_0x01000C5D><se_low>King of tricks: .. What an abhorrent monastery! What a terrible situation!
<voice_0x01000C5E><se_low>King of tricks: The monster was bad enough. But this is the first time I am threatened with torture!
<voice_0x01000C5F><se_low>King of tricks: Excuse me, I'm the king! big king! Just thinking about him makes my blood boil!
<voice_0x01000C61><se_low>January: I don't blame him, a drink at the bar will solve the problem.
<voice_0x01000C62><se_low>January: I just... - How did we end up in this town?
<voice_0x01000C64><se_low>January: Mr. Manager, our city is located in the south of the mainland. how to get there
<voice_0x01000C65><se_low>January: Of course, Beckham is no rose garden. However, it was still a long way off, so even a strange old man like me could get in without any problems.
<voice_0x01000C67><se_low>January: I have a friend who knows everything. We call it the brain. She wants to know more about Domagus' history.
<voice_0x01000C68><se_low>January: Alas, she killed two birds with one stone! More than just a pretty face! reunion! "Give me back my criminal roots!"
